De_Doom_Garden
By SwampyTurtle

Plot: Enter the doom garden. once a well to do garden in the heart of the country, now toxic chemicals have made this place a waste and the repair crews have heard some strange things happening around here with people disappearing and going missing. Discover the secret of the doom garden and live to tell the tale!


CT: stop the hostages from blowing up the haunted garden so that it maybe eveutally restored to working status and discover what happened to the missing workers

T: This damn garden is haunted and we know it. Stop the CT from restoring the garden and bomb the ****  out of the old man Johnsons house, or the patio where evil rituals have take place.
